RB5AUD.original: ~z~Couldn't they make this easy?
RB5_YA_XXX1
RB5_BA
~z~You ain't a biker, asshole - you never will be!
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~你当不了飞车党，混蛋。永远都当不了！

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Don't bust my balls. What's the point of talking about things unless they become real?
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~别跟我扯淡了。讲这种未必发生的事有什么意思？

RB5AUD.original: ~z~well he pays up and he ain't gone state's yet.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~至少他给钱，暂时也没进局子。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Just great. Fantastic.
~z~Here we go again.
RB5_DA
~z~Very funny. Ha, ha.
RB5_ZA
RB5_XA
~z~You were meant to be our messenger.
~z~Shit, your friends body's gonna be smeared from here to Northwood!
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~靠，你朋友的尸体要被一路拖到Northwood了！

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Oh no! Your buddy's dead!
~z~So you're the guy who got jumped for a couple million?
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~你就是被人袭击弄丢几百万的那个？

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Oh, you mean this guy? He's okay...
~z~Listen we got a lot of missing money, and we got a problem with these fucking bikers...
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~听着，我们丢了一大笔钱，还跟那群飞车党有点矛盾...

RB5AUD.original: ~z~The other guys is meant to be taking care of him. Don't worry about it, Nicky.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~会有其他人处理他的。你不用担心，Nicky。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Yeah. You gonna pop me for it?
RB5_CA
~z~-You sure this guy's alright? You checked him out?~n~-I'm tellin' ya the guy's good.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~－你确定这人没问题？你查清楚了？~n~－我说了，这个人很合适。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Even when people forget to tell him about things they're working on...
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~就算忘记跟他汇报工作，也不能不给他钱。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Ha ha... no. I've heard good things. Some aren't friends... but y'know... what are you gonna do?
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~不。久仰久仰。听坏家伙提起过你...你打算怎么办？

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Otherwise, you and Raymond here got a serious problem.
RB5_BC
~z~You took something that belonged to my employers.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~你们拿走了属于我雇主的东西。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Hey, here he is right here. Phil, Niko. Niko, Phil.
~z~The boss has gotta get paid.
~z~You're right... I've been keeping bad company.
~z~Shit, that's the cocksucker that Johnny ripped off for the diamond loot.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~靠，Johnny就是从这个屌毛那儿弄来的钻石钱。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~I got rid of those bikers for you. Johnny wasn't there though.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~飞车党我帮你解决了。不过Johnny没在一起。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Was that the uptown J train?
~z~I couldn't get all of those bikers, Ray. The message hasn't been sent.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~我没能解决所有飞车党，Ray。消息没有送到。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Sure.
~z~Ha! Let's do this!
RB5_EA
~z~How you doing back there, asshole?
~z~maybe you can deal with the bikers. Calm them down.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~飞车党要么你去解决吧。让他们闭嘴。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~I hope you're enjoying yourself.
~z~-Nothing... I mean come on, you're a guy who knows what's what...~n~-Yeah, yeah, yeah, okay.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~－没什么...行啦，你这人该明白的都明白...~n~－行，行，行，行了。

RB5AUD.original: RB5_BB
~z~They're causing trouble on the corner of Vauxite and Exeter.
~z~Now what the hell does that mean?
~z~You ain't never gonna out ride the Lost biker gang.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~你永远都追不上失落摩托帮。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~This thing of ours is only surviving because we send a message when we get fucked with.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~我们能够活到现在，是因为谁敢搞我们，我们就给他警告。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~You've bitten off more than you can chew, dickhead.
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~你碰上啃不动的硬骨头了，屌毛。

RB5AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, I nearly got something on that.
~z~You made a mistake following us.
~z~I'm sure you're sure Phil, you of all people.
~z~So, we sent some of our boys after the money.
~z~Woo hoo! We're riding like real Americans, you ain't!
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~呜呼！我们是纯正美国骑法，你不是！

RB5AUD.original: RB5_AA
~z~Perhaps he was not such a good rider!
RB5_EC
RB5_CB
~z~I'm sure.
RB5_BD
~z~Come back to Drusilla's you amateur.
RB5_EB
~z~Well, the big bad biker got his self killed!
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~好了，大坏蛋骑手把自己给弄死了！

RB5AUD.original: ~z~And I got a problem finding someone.
~z~Hey, why don't we see if he can keep up with some real American bikers?
RB5AUD.translated: ~z~嘿，一起试试他能不能跟上真正的美国飞车党吧？
